Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:23.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:26.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:30.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:34.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.80,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.15,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(460.167,126.389)}The Man-Eating
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(457.167,670.389)}Monster Isoginchack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:30.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the south of the vast\Ncontinent of Africa,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:34.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,countless diamond\Nmines are to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:39.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The area also contains veins\Nof diamonds not yet discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:46.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This man, Kenzo Nakayama,\Nrecently discovered a new diamond vein.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:53.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was writing a letter to his\Nonly relative, a grandson in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:56.34,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:02:01.47,Italics,,0,0,0,,I've never done\Nanything for you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:07.76,Italics,,0,0,0,,but today,\NI am sending you a wonderful gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,The package will\Narrive to you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You found a new diamond mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should give your map to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just sent the\Nmap to my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NTo Hiroshi in Japan, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Shocker cyborg Isoginchack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get back in the\Nocean where you belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the location of the\Ndiamonds, or I'll suck you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see my power now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can suck this in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better get\Nhim to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A persistent pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact the Japan\NBranch at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have my revenge for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of medallion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't there\Nanything else in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.61,0:04:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what the\Npattern means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a\NChristian cross to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter said he'd\Nsend something wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a child's toy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.74,Italics,,0,0,0,,I bet that medallion\Ncontains some kind of secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's take it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be useful later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you! Give that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Policeman, save me!\NThey're thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Thieves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our little Hiroshi\Nis such a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the policeman who just\Ntook over our local police box?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm sure you\Nhaven't heard yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but our boy here likes\Nto play pranks by lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see we need to be a\Nlittle stricter with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not really our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have any family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so we took him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not nice to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to be more\Ntruthful, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all\Nyour hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going on your\Ndelivery job already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he might send some diamonds,\Nbut it was just that hunk of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to put him\Nto work for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However he might look,\NHiroshi's still useful enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What? An anemone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This telegram Hongo\Nsent from Africa says
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that he'll be coming after a\Nboy named Hiroshi Nakayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo will be arriving\Nin Haneda today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?\NHongo's back from Africa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this must be a\Npretty big deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, will you come\Nwith me to see the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dentures, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this clothing\Nis Hiroshi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The remains of an\Nopened package...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It likely contained the\Nmap to the diamond mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means Hiroshi has it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isoginchack, go after him once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All the diamond mines of\NAfrica must belong to Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle? Auntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie? Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Hiroshi, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us the contents of\Nyour package from Africa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't,\NI'll swallow you down and digest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape me, you brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isoginchack! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider...\Nyou'll pay for your meddling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki will soon die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness the power of\NAfrican poison darts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:45.74,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,An antidote Hongo sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It should prove effective...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi wanted me\Nto give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hiroshi now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:11.52,Italics,,0,0,0,,"They seem to want the medallion\Nmy grandfather sent me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,but it's very important to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.94,Italics,,0,0,0,,so I won't let them have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:18.77,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go somewhere\Nthey'll never find me."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nowhere Hiroshi can\Nhide that they won't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where\NHiroshi's hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura,\Nlook after the nice man here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we must find Hiroshi\Nbefore they do at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The place where\NHiroshi is hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To the northwest of his home,\Na place of forests and shrine gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest I leave to your\Ninstincts, Isoginchack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you can\Ncatch his scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It shall be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to help Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:16:00.83,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\an7\c&H000000&\3c&H555B7B&}Jonan Police Umemura Station
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong?\N-They're after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who? Your auntie and uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, an anemone monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,An anemone monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that another silly lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie again,\Nor I'm taking you down to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a boy\Nabout ten years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean 'the boy\Nwho cried wolf'?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Hiroshi Nakayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he played a little\Ntrick on me and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He said an anemone monster was after\Nhim, and ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...\Nare you sure you're up to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right.\N- I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go a little further down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo to Ichimonji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo to Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll meet up with you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:44.71,Italics,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi's destiny is\Nleading him to danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Danger in a high\Nplace," it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A high place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Up a tree, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We almost have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch him at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try and climb up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ring the fire bell\Nand bring everyone running!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... that little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit him with a dart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare they harm Hiroshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! Get him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! Destroy him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've arrived, Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, face us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, look after Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.43,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Double Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a new mission\Nwaiting for me in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay well, Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Hayato to spoil you like\Na real big brother, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:21:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The numbers represent\Ncoordinates on a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kenzo Nakayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa? Are you my grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I got your medallion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Medallion?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need that any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I sold the diamond mine I found
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to return to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to use the money\Nto create a children's home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to help all the sad\Norphans of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wonderful idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to create a\Nlovely children's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know Hiroshi will help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great, Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:59.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's plans to steal the diamond mine\Nthat Kenzo had discovered had been foiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.89,0:23:02.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would continue\Nseeking fresh opportunities to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:04.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,advance their goal\Nof world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:05.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What would they send next?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:08.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And how will Kamen\NRider fight them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:10.76,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:13.95,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.96,0:23:17.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:18.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Kamestone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.35,0:23:22.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The strange beams\Nemitted by Kamestone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:24.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,create a deadly aurora.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:26.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:31.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Monstrous Kamestone's\NKiller Aurora Plan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:31.49,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(447.167,740.389)}The Monstrous Kamestone's\NKiller Aurora Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:41.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:43.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:45.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:51.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:53.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:54.86,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:56.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:04.42,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:08.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:11.67,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:15.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Man-Eating\NMonster Isoginchack